imdb.plot outline: Hungry? Then it's time to meet the California Dream Eater, a culinary connoisseur in search of dream eats across the state. The best part is, he's taking orders. Tell him what you dream of eating in California and he will hunt it down and eat it for you, right in front of your face. Because that's what dream eaters do.
